{"type": "article", "id": 26181, "title": "灵感源自日本太鼓的家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-29T07:23:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607183857rgcMxJQO2Bo7zidC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">Miles Endo 是 <a href=\"http://www.studioendo.com/\" target=\"_blank\">STUDIO ENDO</a> 的一名设计师，他的父母都是日本太鼓手。以此为灵感，他设计了这套名为 <a href=\"http://api.viglink.com/api/click?format=go&amp;jsonp=vglnk_146182645604014&amp;key=6ab1d62aaf9dbafae96546ba3ca1b2ac&amp;libId=injwmbx50100x1tt000DL1ey6e7yoscvks&amp;loc=http%3A%2F%2Fdesign-milk.com%2Fhira-collection-inspired-japanese-taiko-drums%2F&amp;v=1&amp;out=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.studioendo.com%2Fcollections%2Fhira-lighting-series&amp;title=Furnishings%20Inspired%20by%20Taiko%20Drums%20-%20Design%20Milk&amp;txt=HIRA\">HIRA</a> 的家具包含了一系列灯具和媒体柜，采用铜和仿乌木作为主要的制作材料，传递出了日系的简约和典雅。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607183855YaTbQkzeUX1n3od7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607183856cMQYyEsm162TaOfo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607183856Px3zoMekLRVZfAal.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071838572c4jkJnd0rS8mDzq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}